<p>People love to talk about how much it costs to raise children. And it's true. Babies cost money and it can be a difficult adjustment as you try to manage new expenses along with a new life. But sometimes I think there's too much focus on the struggle. With the right mindset, I actually believe that new parents are in the perfect financial situation.
